modShortDescription: Just a simple mod to add steel casings to the game. Mostly for servers with a large player base. 5 casings per steel ingot.
modDescription:
Just a simple mod to add steel [casings](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-ammo/) to the game. Mostly for servers with a large player base. 5 casings per steel ingot.

**[Download](https://github.com/VerucaKatt/Steel-Casings/archive/refs/heads/main.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/24644-steel-casings-mod/).
